# .copilotignore -- Copilot content exclusion.
#
# CRITICAL LIMITATION: these exclusions apply to IDE inline suggestions and
# Copilot Chat context ONLY. They do NOT apply to Copilot CLI, the coding
# agent, or IDE agent/edit modes -- those surfaces can still read every path
# below. Sandbox mode (working-dir restriction), the --deny-tool wrapper,
# the preToolUse hook, and Gitleaks/detect-secrets pre-commit scanning are
# the compensating controls for agent surfaces.

# Secrets and credentials
.env
.env.*
**/secrets/**
**/credentials/**
appsettings.*.json
**/certificates/**
*.pfx
*.pem
*.key

# Client-specific directories (update per engagement)
**/client-confidential/**

# Infrastructure secrets
**/terraform.tfvars
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.backup
